  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the curry powder, turmeric, and cumin and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the squash and cook until tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Stir in the lime juice and salt.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh cilantro if desired.",
    "Let it cool for a few minutes before serving.",
    "Serve with rice or roti for a filling meal."
